CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 25, 1960, pg. A11 reads: "11. The winner of the Atlas Portable Sewing Machine, Helen Thomas, second from right [on right], is surrounded by happy representatives Mickey Margulies, Bette Lou Poling, Kriss Graham, William J. Carlson and Sir Walter, M.C., from WAMO"
